    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >养殖场最近发生了很多离奇的怪事：流血的水龙头、长出头颅的闹钟、敲门的人皮......<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/7f403036d7347d17166eb1dddda0dbdc.poster.avif?t=1769941615\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/7f403036d7347d17166eb1dddda0dbdc.webm?t=1769941615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/7f403036d7347d17166eb1dddda0dbdc.mp4?t=1769941615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>怪物一次又一次发起进攻，你将扮演一名弱小的保安，逃避怪物追击的同时，调查它们出现的原因。 <br>在此期间，你能通过电脑监控来守关，以获得拥有神奇功能的道具： <br>无人机，在第一人称和第三人称视角之间自由切换<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/e9a4b9b6bc4c5dfc5bf987123483cafd.avif?t=1769941615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras_big/e9a4b9b6bc4c5dfc5bf987123483cafd.avif?t=1769941615 width=800 height=800 /></span>打火机，夜晚探索时必不可少的道具<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/05d7ddf1532e6ee6408e4a519e868cf1.poster.avif?t=1769941615\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/05d7ddf1532e6ee6408e4a519e868cf1.webm?t=1769941615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/05d7ddf1532e6ee6408e4a519e868cf1.mp4?t=1769941615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>认识足以称得上生死之交的朋友<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras/edc7739874199f61c1bb9217dd815cf3.avif?t=1769941615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171340/extras_big/edc7739874199f61c1bb9217dd815cf3.avif?t=1769941615 width=800 height=800 /></span>在朋友们的帮助下，来到大山乐园，查明事情的真相，打败真正的幕后黑手，成为世界人民的靠山。 <br>购买本游戏后，你将体验恐怖游戏和动作游戏带来的双重刺激。 <br>敌人的防御方式各不相同，使用神奇道具，应对未知的怪物。</p>",
